GenerationOfBankRemittance is a BusinessTask
    owned by dt

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            Reports
                GenerationOfBankRemittanceReport

    Parameters
        Company                 is a ReceivableCompany
        ProcessLevel            is a ReceivableProcessLevel
        CashCode
        RemitType               is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                All        value is blank
                Encashed   value is "E"
                Discounted value is "D"
        RemitDate               is Date
        FrMaturityDate          is Date
        ToMaturityDate          is Date
        PrintOption             is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Print   value is "P"
                Reprint value is "R"
        ReprintRemitNbr         is Numeric size 7

    Parameter Rules
        Company
            required
        ProcessLevel
            required
        PrintOption
        	initial value is "P"
            default to "P"

    Actions
        GenerationOfBankRemittance is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
